Thank you to everyone who reached out!! All slots have been filled, so I‚Äôm going to close this. I am currently working on getting back to everyone who has made a request and making sure I‚Äôve got info and donations squared away~ Thank you again for all your support!

Though in the grand scheme of things it might not be much, I want to do what I can to help the AAPI community. My good friend @jameslien and I will be taking drawing requests for donations over $30 (please see his post for additional details)~

My employer is double matching my donations, so all proceeds plus 200% extra will be given to AALDEF (Asian American Legal Defense & Education Fund. AALDEF is a national organization that protects and promotes the civil rights of Asian Americans by combining litigation, advocacy and education to secure human rights for all.
